CPC Senior Official Meets Guatemalan Party leader
BEIJING , February 27 ( Xinhua ) -- Wen Jiabao , a member of the Political Bureau and a member of the Secretariat of the Communist Party of China ( CPC ) Central Committee , met here this afternoon with a delegation from the National Revolutionary Union ( NRU ) of Guatemala led by General Secretary Ricardo Ramirez .
Wen said China supports the peace process in Guatemala , expressing the hope that Guatemala can score more progress , and welcomes more Guatemalan friends to China to enhance mutual understanding .
The CPC hopes to develop friendly relations with the Guatemalan NRU , he added .
Wen also briefed the visitors on China 's current domestic situation .
Ramirez gave an introduction of his party and Guatemala 's domestic conditions .
The delegation is here as guest of the International Department of CPC Central Committee .
Deputy Head of the International Department of the CPC Central Committee Liu Jingqin held working talks with the delegation after their arrival in Beijing on February 24 .
